---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Growth Map | Fractional COO & Business Operations Consulting"
  description="Growth Map helps founders replace chaos with clarity. Fractional COO services, operating systems, and growth strategy for businesses doing $1M-$10M in revenue."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1200px] flex-col items-center gap-12 md:flex-row md:gap-16">
      <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
          Grow Revenue without the chaos
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-navy sm:text-4xl md:text-[56px] md:leading-[1.1]">
          Running Your Business Shouldn't Feel This Hard
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-mid-gray md:text-xl">
          I help founders get unstuck, focus their business, and grow without burning out.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
          <a
            href="https://calendar.notion.so/meet/cameronearloliver/qc3y04oud"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
          >
            Book a Free Consult
          </a>
          <a
            href="/time-audit"
            class="inline-block rounded-lg border-2 border-navy px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-navy transition-colors hover:bg-navy hover:text-white"
          >
            Take the Free Time Audit
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/images/headshot.jpeg"
          alt="Cameron Oliver, founder of Growth Map"
          class="w-72 rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:w-80"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CURRENT SITUATION (Stark: "Current Situation") -->
  <section class="bg-light-gray px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        This Is Where You Are Right Now
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-mid-gray">Sound familiar?</p>
      <ul class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-left">
        {[
          "You're the only person who can make decisions, and it's crushing your calendar.",
          "You've hired good people, but they still come to you for everything.",
          "Revenue is flat or unpredictable, and you're not sure why.",
          "You're working harder than ever, but the business isn't growing faster.",
          "You're carrying the weight of the entire company — and it's bleeding into nights, weekends, and your health.",
        ].map((item) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-dark-text">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue" />
            {item}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DESIRED FUTURE STATE (Stark: "Desired Future State") -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        What You Actually Want
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-left">
        {[
          "A team that owns outcomes — not one that hands you problems to solve.",
          "Clarity on exactly what's driving revenue and how to grow it.",
          "Weeks that feel calm, focused, and intentional — not reactive.",
          "Decisions based on real data instead of gut instinct and guesswork.",
          "A business that grows without depending on you to hold everything together.",
        ].map((item) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-dark-text">
            <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-bright-blue" />
            {item}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BRIDGE: YOUR CONTRIBUTION (Stark: "Perceived Contribution") -->
  <section class="bg-light-gray px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] text-center">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
        How Growth Map Helps
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        I Help You Build the System That Makes This Possible
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
        Growth Map is a fractional COO practice. I work with founders to figure out what's actually driving their business, who should own what, and how to build a rhythm that replaces chaos with clarity. Most clients go from overwhelmed to in-control within 90 days.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/time-audit"
        class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
      >
        Find Out Where You're Stuck →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES (Outcome-focused, incremental ladder) -->
  <section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px]">
      <p class="mb-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
        How We Work Together
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        Three Ways to Start
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-center text-lg text-mid-gray">Most clients start with a Diagnostic and move into a Build.</p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Card 1 — Entry -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-light-gray p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-mid-gray">Step 1</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Growth Map Diagnostic</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-dark-text">
            Walk away knowing exactly what's stalling your growth and the 2-3 moves that will move revenue.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
            A 30-60 minute deep-dive where we map how your business actually creates value, identify what's broken, and give you a clear action plan — not a 50-page report.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 — Core -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border-2 border-bright-blue bg-light-gray p-8 relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 rounded-full bg-bright-blue px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white">Most Popular</div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-mid-gray">Step 2</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-navy">The Growth Map Build</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-dark-text">
            In 90 days, your team runs the business without you being the bottleneck on every decision.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
            Everything from the Diagnostic, plus: we build your operating system together — roles, ownership, scorecard, weekly rhythm. You stop managing by inbox and start leading with clarity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 — Ongoing -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-light-gray p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-mid-gray">Step 3</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-navy">Fractional COO</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-dark-text">
            Your business grows quarter over quarter because someone owns the operating system — not you.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-mid-gray">
            Everything from the Build, plus: I stay on as your operating partner. I run the system, drive improvements, and keep the team aligned — so you can focus on the work only you can do.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-mid-gray">Not sure which is right for you?</p>
        <a
          href="https://calendar.notion.so/meet/cameronearloliver/qc3y04oud"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-4 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
        >
          Book a Free Consult
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY NOW (Stark: Urgency / cost of inaction) -->
  <section class="bg-navy px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] text-center">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">The Cost of Waiting</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-white md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        Every Month You Stay the Bottleneck Costs You More Than You Think
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 text-left sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-bright-blue">10-20 hrs</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">per week that founders spend on work someone else could do — time that never goes to growth</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-bright-blue">6-12 months</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">is how long most founders wait before getting help — after the damage is already done</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/10 p-6">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-bright-blue">$100K+</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70">in lost revenue from bad hires, unclear priorities, and decisions made on instinct instead of insight</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/time-audit"
        class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-10 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
      >
        See Where Your Time Goes →
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-white/50">Free. No email required. Results in 3 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CEO TIME AUDIT CTA -->
  <section class="bg-light-gray px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-center">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-bright-blue">
        Start Here
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-[40px] md:leading-tight">
        Find Out Where Your Time Actually Goes
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text">
        Most founders spend over half their week on $10/hr work. The CEO Time Audit breaks your week into $10, $100, $1,000, and $10,000-per-hour tasks — so you can see where to focus and what to hand off.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/time-audit"
        class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-lg bg-bright-blue px-10 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#0088c2]"
      >
        Take the CEO Time Audit →
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-mid-gray">3 minutes. No email required.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
